## Proposed Changes

### Component 1 — Backend: Domain / Entities

#### [MODIFY] Appointment.cs
- Make `StartTime` and `EndTime` **nullable** (`DateTime?`)
- Add `QueueNumber` (int) — sequential per clinic per day
- Add `DoctorAssignedTime` (DateTime?) — doctor sets this after booking

#### [MODIFY] Clinic.cs
- Add `MaxAppointmentsPerDay` (int?) — null = unlimited

---

### Component 2 — Backend: DTOs

#### [MODIFY] AppointmentDTOs.cs
- `AppointmentDto`: Add `QueueNumber`, `DoctorAssignedTime`; make `StartTime`/`EndTime` nullable
- `CreateAppointmentDto`: Remove `StartTime`, `EndTime` (no longer needed from patient)
- **[NEW]** `DayAvailabilityDto`: `{ Date, BookedCount, MaxCapacity, RemainingSlots, IsFull }`
- **[NEW]** `AssignAppointmentTimeDto`: `{ DoctorAssignedTime, Comment }`

